# The ONLY AUR packages in this setup, and only on the work machine.
# xrdp is required there: locked-down Windows clients can only use mstsc/RDP.

xrdp
xorgxrdp

# NOTE: pulseaudio-module-xrdp is deliberately absent — its PKGBUILD conflicts
# with pipewire-pulse and would rip out the PipeWire stack. If RDP-session
# audio is ever needed, pipewire-module-xrdp (AUR) is the PipeWire-native
# path — uncomment below.
# pipewire-module-xrdp
